  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/coretext\/kctfontdownloadableattribute\ncrawled: 2026-03-10T14:39:09Z\n---\n\n# kCTFontDownloadableAttribute\n\n**Global Variable**\n\nThe font downloadable state.\n\n## Declaration\n\n```swift\nlet kCTFontDownloadableAttribute: CFString\n```\n\n## Discussion\n\nThe value associated with this key is a [doc:\/\/com.apple.documentation\/documentation\/CoreFoundation\/CFBoolean].  If it is [doc:\/\/com.apple.documentation\/documentation\/CoreFoundation\/kCFBooleanTrue], Core Text attempts to download a font if necessary when matching a descriptor.\n\n## Constants\n\n- **ATSFONTREF_DEFINED**\n- **kBSLNIdeographicHighBaseline**\n- **kCTAdaptiveImageProviderAttributeName**\n- **kCTBackgroundColorAttributeName**\n- **kCTBaselineClassAttributeName**\n- **kCTBaselineClassHanging**\n- **kCTBaselineClassIdeographicCentered**\n- **kCTBaselineClassIdeographicHigh**\n- **kCTBaselineClassIdeographicLow**\n- **kCTBaselineClassMath**\n- **kCTBaselineClassRoman**\n- **kCTBaselineInfoAttributeName**\n- **kCTBaselineOriginalFont**\n- **kCTBaselineReferenceFont**\n- **kCTBaselineReferenceInfoAttributeName**\n\n",
